Enum Class Element

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Element>
edu.uoc.nertia.model.cells.Element
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Element>, Constable
public enum Element extends Enum<Element>
Enumeration that represents the type of element that can be housed by a cell.

David García Solórzano
